{"tid":1405730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日幫人罷工活動細節！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-04T10:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T11:58:27.000Z","uid":238467,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"de49aee4ecc941e36b670779f65c721bb12f8445","tid":1405730,"uid":238467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:58:10.000Z","msg":"我完全明白有好多人同手足無辦法咁方便罷工<br />\n而唔洗擔心 我地係會幫你地罷嘅！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n但係我地做緊野嘅同時<br />\n係需要有人做以下幾樣重要嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一 好似上次嘅不合作運動咁<br />\n一定會有人話我地係做緊同民意相反嘅事<br />\n請各位打工仔同手足請唔好吝嗇你地嘅掌聲同歡呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁班藍絲奴工就會收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二 各位手足 請保持冷靜<br />\n我地做自己野就得 必要時 問下現場有無人支持<br />\n到時就會有第一點嘅人幫手<br />\n盡量避免直接開佢波<br />\n人地開我地波嘅話 咁就識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三 唔係前線嘅手足<br />\n做文宣！！！ 可以大聲播鏗鏘集<br />\n可以大聲播立場 乜都得<br />\n強迫佢地睇 脫離TVB嘅魔爪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 叫大家罷工去七區集會<br />\n返屋企換套衫好 直接去又好<br />\n基本上有齊不反對通知書<br />\n和理非同伴請放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求！！！！！<br />\n缺一不何！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以幫我推下<br />\n聽日就係喇 想集中下意見<br />\n大家有意見都可以提出討論 <br />\nThank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EW1V78v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEW1V78v.png&h=f3be1ae3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3aa9525c0f304db63da9dbd8b219e353f6fbf95","tid":1405730,"uid":238467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de49aee4ecc941e36b670779f65c721bb12f8445","tid":1405730,"uid":238467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:58:10.000Z","msg":"我完全明白有好多人同手足無辦法咁方便罷工<br />\n而唔洗擔心 我地係會幫你地罷嘅！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n但係我地做緊野嘅同時<br />\n係需要有人做以下幾樣重要嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一 好似上次嘅不合作運動咁<br />\n一定會有人話我地係做緊同民意相反嘅事<br />\n請各位打工仔同手足請唔好吝嗇你地嘅掌聲同歡呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁班藍絲奴工就會收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二 各位手足 請保持冷靜<br />\n我地做自己野就得 必要時 問下現場有無人支持<br />\n到時就會有第一點嘅人幫手<br />\n盡量避免直接開佢波<br />\n人地開我地波嘅話 咁就識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三 唔係前線嘅手足<br />\n做文宣！！！ 可以大聲播鏗鏘集<br />\n可以大聲播立場 乜都得<br />\n強迫佢地睇 脫離TVB嘅魔爪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 叫大家罷工去七區集會<br />\n返屋企換套衫好 直接去又好<br />\n基本上有齊不反對通知書<br />\n和理非同伴請放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求！！！！！<br />\n缺一不何！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以幫我推下<br />\n